<h1>Installation</h1>

<p>
  To use the theme you need to install it by running the following command in
  your terminal.
</p>

<pre><code>$ ember install ember-uikit-adsy-theme</code></pre>

This will install <code>uikit</code> and <code>ember-cli-sass</code>. To
include the styles in your application you need to add the following import
at the start of your <code>/app/styles/app.scss</code>.

<pre><code>@import 'ember-uikit-adsy-theme'</code></pre>

If you want to customize any of the variables, define them before importing
the addon.

<pre><code>$global-primary-background: #ff00ff;

// any other variable definitions

@import 'ember-uikit-adsy-theme';</code></pre>